ncing<br />\n你問target 佢通常都hea 答同唔比data<br />\n<br />\n所以FDD 啲skill set 好廢<br />\nForecast 又唔識financial modeling 又唔識business 又掂得唔多<br />\n但其實呢啲先最重要<br />\n<br />\n對於岩岩audit 出黎嘅人一開頭會覺得FDD好有用<br />\n而家啲人用stat 去做分析, 用coding 去build data pack<br />\n唔係好似香港咁逐個analysis 砌<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係喺個井底太耐唔個出面做緊咩野，<br />\n先覺得自己喺香港好學到嘢？"},{"pid":"9574d0b417509e1fbd964245b1cd2498c5500bd4","tid":1595114,"uid":64870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cac011eb7da9975fc150712a13efddc70278c60","tid":1595114,"uid":159934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92d24ca453430cb1ae332487697d593c507b303c","tid":1595114,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf35ed70be7fd4f3009cd36cd988b3c107d1cd67","tid":1595114,"uid":159934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"有opening咪報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:14:52.000Z","msg":"今年真係唔多樂觀<br />\n發夢聽到有一間firm deals某啲grade normal pay 全部冇得升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"咁慘...我聽有間直情freeze咗headcount"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T14:49:08.000Z","msg":"jpm?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b5b172c17ff5b6df07ac322fbc270ce3201369","tid":1595114,"uid":159934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8eba06427fe564fb0844e4a5a01024413cef2b2a","tid":1595114,"uid":72541,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"00b54fa07280e33273dbd6d99bc109c1670de4a3","tid":1595114,"uid":159934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"696b752521b1ef2f8ad6ac7d29b4d04341549265","tid":1595114,"uid":72541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"做FDD 真係好唔value-added<br />\n啲pro-forma adjustments 好多都好無聊<br />\n個人覺得真係早走早著<br />\n<br />\nBtw 香港啲PE Fund working hours 係唔係好癲？<br />\n<br />\n利申：做咗FDD 1.5 年, 不過唔係香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"點無聊法先, adjustment係要剔走non recurring item, 減走target唔啱或者加番漏咗既item,對於PE firm modeling上係幾有幫助<br />\n<br />\n而且report仲會summarize哂所有bank loan main customer vendor agreements 去assess target risk and sustainability, 做revenue COGS staff cost trend analysis 同forecast, 亦會向client提出before during post transaction建議, 而client真係會認真研究同考慮<br />\n<br />\n我唔會話fdd好value adding, but at least 有用過audit好多倍同自己會學到好多野,況且唔value adding佢做咩要搵你做fdd先,都冇regulations逼你做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪你喺日本學唔到野咋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"你要做adjustment 都要人地QA/interview 認真答你你先做到架<br />\n<br />\nFDD 又淨係睇過去<br />\n將來有影響嘅impact 大部分都話non-quantifiable 跟住寫幾句解釋就算<br />\n<br />\nRevenue/COGS 呢啲你通常只會identify 個trend, 但無business data 去support 其實好唔convincing<br />\n你問target 佢通常都hea 答同唔比data<br />\n<br />\n所以FDD 啲skill set 好廢<br />\nForecast 又唔識financial modeling 又唔識business 又掂得唔多<br />\n但其實呢啲先最重要<br />\n<br />\n對於岩岩audit 出黎嘅人一開頭會覺得FDD好有用<br />\n而家啲人用stat 去做分析, 用coding 去build data pack<br />\n唔係好似香港咁逐個analysis 砌<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係喺個井底太耐唔個出面做緊咩野，<br />\n先覺得自己喺香港好學到嘢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"對於一個初入行者, fdd真係一個幾好既學習機會同跳板, 你連basic foundation都未打好點做forecast financial modeling<br />\n<br />\n而且我同你喺fdd做既project都唔同,何解可以一概而論? 我某d project就真係會分析forecast同用business data do trend analysis,並唔只係空談同focus過去<br />\n<br />\n咩係喺個井底太耐? 唔好諗到個個都同你年資一樣先,對於一個遠少過2年經驗點會係耐  <br />\n<br />\nanyways既然你係外面做緊M&amp;A related既野,希望你都可以同我地分享下心得,幫下大家"},{"pid":"2ee0b2d0228172e55fe2d08e23e2e0733756c8f6","tid":1595114,"uid":96485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"巴打請指點吓<br />\n出面睇3+3多啲定係big 4 mgr title多啲？"},